NPM

NPM is a packer manager for Node.js packages or modules.
NPM program is installed on your computer when you install node.js

A package in node.js contains all files you need for a module.
Modules are javascript libraries you can include in your project.

npm install upper-case

upperscase module is installed and you can use it in ur application.

var uc=require('upper-case');
res.write(uc.upperCase("Hello World!"));

